{"id":600635,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/11/【立此存照】b站开倒车视频纷纷禁评/","date":"2018-11-29T10:48:02Z","modified":"2018-11-30T08:24:35Z","title":"【立此存照】B站“开倒车”视频纷纷“禁评”","content":"<p>11月29日，有网友爆料，国内知名视频网站bilibili近日将所有“开倒车”视频的搜索结果纷纷禁止了评论，无论是何种视频题材，只要是标题或描述中含有“开倒车”字样，一律“禁评”&#8230;&#8230;有网友询问客服禁评的原因，被告知“因包含题材敏感的梗 比较难解释”。</p>\n<p>下图为B站关键词“开倒车”的搜索结果<a href=\"https://search.bilibili.com/all?keyword=%E5%BC%80%E5%80%92%E8%BD%A6&amp;from_source=banner_search\">第一页</a>，此页面内的视频均被禁评。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600637\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"552\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车.jpg 1274w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车-300x276.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车-768x707.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车-1024x942.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>与时政题材毫无关联的科技、游戏、体育内容，仅因标题包含“开倒车”则被禁评。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600638\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"306\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车2.jpg 1512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车2-300x153.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车2-768x392.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车2-1024x523.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600639\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车3.jpg 1507w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车3-300x156.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车3-768x400.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车3-1024x533.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600640\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车4.jpg 1523w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车4-300x139.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车4-768x356.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车4-1024x474.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600641\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车5.jpg 1513w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车5-300x142.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车5-768x364.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车5-1024x486.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>ID名以及视频描述包含“开倒车”关键词，同样被禁评。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600642\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车6.jpg 1500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车6-300x152.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车6-768x390.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/开倒车6-1024x520.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></p>\n<p>网友询问客服“禁评”原因所得到的答复。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-600644\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzAYxU8AAg1Of.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzAYxU8AAg1Of.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzAYxU8AAg1Of-150x300.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-600643 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzBeKUcAAIivj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzBeKUcAAIivj.jpg 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/11/DtIzBeKUcAAIivj-150x300.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p>搜索<a href=\"https://search.bilibili.com/all?keyword=%E5%BC%80%E5%80%92%E8%BD%A6&amp;from_source=banner_search\">结果 </a>传送门</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/07/%e5%a2%99%e5%a4%96%e6%a5%bc-%e5%8f%b8%e6%9c%ba%e5%9c%a8%e9%ab%98%e9%80%9f%e4%b8%8a%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6-%e8%a2%ab%e8%bf%bd%e5%b0%be%e5%8f%91%e7%94%9f%e6%83%a8%e5%89%a7/\">墙外楼 | 司机在高速上开倒车 被追尾发生惨剧</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e7%bd%91%e5%88%a0%e9%99%a4%e9%80%94%e8%a7%82tg%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6%e4%b8%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%be%ae/\">【立此存照】人民网删除“途观(TG)开倒车下台”微博</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/11/%e7%8e%8b%e6%80%9d%e6%83%b3%e5%ae%b6-%e5%8d%97%e8%bd%a6%e5%8c%97%e8%bd%a6%e4%b8%80%e8%b5%b7%e5%bc%80%e5%80%92%e8%bd%a6/\">王思想家 | 南车北车一起开倒车</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n","author":974,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32862,9526,26869,13222,37051,32273,31267,37050,9212,10088]}